Marie Walcamp https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie_Walcamp 0 Marie Walcamp (July 27, 1894 – November 17, 1936) was an American actress of the silent film era, often specializing in roles as an "action heroine" in serials, including Westerns.
